title: Kitsu's Furry Collection (OCT 08) [KiTSU]
description:
This is a collection of all my sorted furry stuff, I intend to add more as time
goes on, ill try to preserve the directory structure so torrents can be
replaced and you wont have to download files you already have.

This contains alot of furry comics, art CDs, videos and furry manga (Japanese
comics), please note that they are in CBR format, which is actually just a
renamed RAR file, but you should use a CBR viewer program such as CDisplayEx
to read them.

Assume that all the furry Manga is in Japanese language, unless specified
otherwise, everything else is in English.

I encourage that you redistribute these files on other file-sharing networks,
but I ask that you keep the filenames and content as they are, but this is the
internet, so whatever.

If you enjoy the artist's work, I suggest that you make a donation to them.

October 2008

Kitsu~
